 profile showed larger variation in lateral direction and corresponded to the soil thickness distribution better than the P-wave velocity (V p) profile by SR. The combined use of ERI and SWM may be more effective in detecting the soil-bedrock interface because each method compensates for the deficiencies of the other method. {\textcopyright} 2011 Elsevier B.V.},
