ngly improved model performance with respect to the baseflow. Further, MWARPE consistently led to the best baseflow estimates for the three models, while the HBV model resulted in the best simulations of the baseflow, regardless of the calibration algorithm. The overall conclusion of this paper is that, even though it may be difficult to assess which model and calibration algorithm resulted in the best discharge estimates, the MWARPE calibration algorithm and the HBV model consistently led to the best internal model dynamics. ?? 2009 Elsevier B.V. All rights reserved.},
